   8 items, all Willpower primary (+8 WP on base ~10 = 18 WP total)
   Secondaries: ~6x Penetration (+1.00 ea) + ~2x Spell (+0.34 ea)
   Derived stats:
     Pen = WP + Pen_bonus = 18 + 6 = 24
     Res = WP + 0         = 18
     MaxSpells = Int(10)/3 + 0.68 = ~4.0
     MaxActions = Str(10)/3 = ~3.33
     MaxBody = Str(10) * 50 = 500
     MaxMind = Int(10) * 50 = 500
