====================================================================
 GAME FORMULAS (from Tooltip.js source)
====================================================================
   Attack damage  = base * (1 + (Hit   - Evasion)   * 0.10)
   Spell damage   = base * (1 + (Pen   - Resistance) * 0.10)
   MaxBody        = Strength * 50 + Body_bonus
   MaxMind        = Intelligence * 50 + Mind_bonus
   MaxActions     = Strength / 3  + Action_bonus     (regen PER MINUTE)
   MaxSpells      = Intelligence / 3 + Spell_bonus
   Spell regen    = MaxSpells / 9 per non-spell attack

   Block chance   = 100 - Lust%
     => When block triggers: ALL damage (attacks AND spells) hits Mind
        before Body. Body only takes overflow once Mind = 0.
     => At Lust=0% (fight start): 100% block. Everything hits Mind first.
   Mindless       = Mind=0 OR Lust=100% (no block, ailments land freely)

   CRITICAL IMPLICATION:
     Your physical attacks also hit the opponent's Mind before Body.
     At Lust=0% they have 100% block. You must drain their Mind (500)
     BEFORE you can damage their Body (500).
     REAL KILL TARGET = MaxMind + MaxBody = 500 + 500 = 1000

 ENCHANT VALUES (per item slot):
   Primary:   Strength, Dexterity, Intelligence, Willpower = +1.00 each
   Secondary: Hit, Evasion, Penetration, Resistance        = +1.00 each
              Mind, Body                                    = +50  each
              Spell, Action                                 = +0.34 each

 BASE STATS ASSUMED (mid-tier character):
   Str=10, Dex=10, Int=10, WP=10
   => Body=500, Mind=500, MaxActions=3.33, MaxSpells=3.33

====================================================================
 BASE DAMAGE VALUES
====================================================================
   Base attack damage: ~50
   Base spell  damage: ~120

   Opponent Pen=24 vs your Res=10:
     Spell mult = 1 + (24-10) * 0.10 = x2.4
     => Each spell = 120 * 2.4 = 288 damage to YOUR Mind (then Body)

   Their 4-spell burst = 4 * 288 = 1152 raw damage
   Your Mind (500) absorbs 500. Overflow = 652 to Body.
   If your Body < 652 you die in the burst. Need Body > 652.

   Opponent's own kill target against YOU = your Mind + your Body.
   Their DPS = 288 * cycle_rate + attacks. Very high.

====================================================================
 THE REAL KILL MATH (corrected)
====================================================================
 KILL TARGET = opponent Mind (500) + opponent Body (500) = 1000

   Simplified: Body damage on target = total_dmg_you_deal - their_MaxMind
   Their Mind absorbs the first 500 damage you deal regardless of source.

