   Survivor (2WP+3Dex+3Str 4Res+2Hit+2Action): 75 * 5.01 = 376/min => 1000 in ~160s

 Their damage clock:
   Burst 1 fires at t~54s (3 attacks done). Full burst = 4 spells.
   Total incoming during burst = depends on your Res:
     No Res build: 3 * attack_dmg + 4 * 288
     With Res=16 (Survivor): 3 * 35 + 4 * 216 = 969

